00:49:43.974 --> 00:49:45.360
AUDIENCE: How's it going?

00:49:45.360 --> 00:49:48.540
What's are thesis with
regards to active management

00:49:48.540 --> 00:49:52.776
of your acquisitions, be it
real estate or businesses?

00:49:55.700 --> 00:49:57.550
BRUCE FLATT: To the
asset management of it?

00:49:57.550 --> 00:50:01.140
AUDIENCE: Yes, so like when
you purchase general growth

00:50:01.140 --> 00:50:03.150
or build a mall,
are you coming in

00:50:03.150 --> 00:50:05.670
